sweet and expensive, capiche?

41
00:01:48,358 --> 00:01:49,234
No capiche.

42
00:01:49,317 --> 00:01:51,986
Lona, I don't have the energy,
I don't have the time.

43
00:01:52,070 --> 00:01:53,923
