what club you're here...

44
00:01:53,947 --> 00:01:55,281
- Debate!
- Debate!

45
00:01:55,365 --> 00:01:57,158
Go. Out. Scram.

46
00:01:57,242 --> 00:01:58,243
Shoo!

47
00:01:58,326 --> 00:01:59,494
Go talk to Kathy.

48
00:02:01,204 --> 00:02:02,831
