Well, yes. Wait, yes!

95
00:05:12,687 --> 00:05:15,606
I was gonna talk about lasting
relationships, but kissing is better.

96
00:05:15,690 --> 00:05:18,693
Forget Yale.
Focus on becoming a better kisser.

97
00:05:18,776 --> 00:05:21,738
