- You want me to write it?

98
00:05:21,821 --> 00:05:23,239
The world needs good men

99
00:05:23,323 --> 00:05:24,824
- who know how to kiss.
- [sighs]

100
00:05:24,907 --> 00:05:26,659
I'm dead serious.
Are you writing this down?

101
00:05:26,743 --> 00:05:27,845
- No!
- [Bennett] Well, you should,

102
