190
00:09:28,609 --> 00:09:32,029
This is a skilled event based on research,
memorization and execution,

191
00:09:32,113 --> 00:09:33,739
where I am in charge of my own destiny.

192
00:09:33,823 --> 00:09:36,117
- It's not about luck.
- Obviously.

193
00:09:36,909 --> 00:09:39,870
I'm gonna go jump in the coffee
and make some shower.

194
00:09:42,081 --> 00:09:44,601
