200
00:09:56,012 --> 00:09:57,221
I'm really well.

201
00:09:57,305 --> 00:09:59,181
My daughter is the co-president

202
00:09:59,265 --> 00:10:01,267
of the Hemlock Prep Academy
Debate Club, so...

203
00:10:01,350 --> 00:10:03,894
