Co-presidents?

204
00:10:03,978 --> 00:10:06,355
Well, I'm just glad
it all worked out in the end.

205
00:10:06,439 --> 00:10:09,066
Actually, I don't think it worked out.
I think Lona deserved it.

206
00:10:10,192 --> 00:10:12,528
