00:11:26,560 --> 00:11:28,521
It's going great. Thanks, Lona.

228
00:11:28,604 --> 00:11:29,438
How are you?

229
00:11:29,522 --> 00:11:31,941
I'm just glad you're judging
and not sitting over there.

230
00:11:32,024 --> 00:11:34,318
