You pick the lie.

347
00:17:09,028 --> 00:17:11,488
- So you'll mail it out for me?
- Oh, no, no.

348
00:17:11,572 --> 00:17:13,824
You have to take this down
to the school mailbox

349
00:17:13,907 --> 00:17:14,742
and mail it yourself.

350
00:17:14,825 --> 00:17:16,410
