[alarm ringing]

953
00:48:21,690 --> 00:48:23,358
[door squeaking]

954
00:48:26,028 --> 00:48:27,195
[Lona groans]

955
00:48:28,071 --> 00:48:28,989
[Amy] I'm sorry.

