00:48:49,259 --> 00:48:50,385
[sighs]

961
00:48:51,386 --> 00:48:53,388
[Julia]
Well, he's the valedictorian of his class

962
00:48:53,472 --> 00:48:57,559
and a living president
wrote his letter of recommendation.

963
00:48:57,643 --> 00:48:59,853
Look, I'm not saying
that you made a mistake,

964
00:48:59,936 --> 00:49:02,147
but I wouldn't be surprised if you had.

965
00:49:02,230 --> 00:49:05,359
No, I'm not trying to tell you
how to run your institution,

966
00:49:05,442 --> 00:49:08,695
but as an alumnus, I'm saying
I'm exceptionally disappointed

967
00:49:08,779 --> 00:49:10,072
by your decision.

968
00:49:10,155 --> 00:49:14,618
Well, obviously, you're forgetting
that I contributed $100,000...

969
00:49:15,410 --> 00:49:17,329
- [Bennett] Are you out of your mind?
- Bennett.

970
00:49:17,412 --> 00:49:20,207
- You're not helping.
