973
00:49:25,879 --> 00:49:27,589
It's not that simple... Bennett.

974
00:49:27,673 --> 00:49:30,425
Bennett, it's never that simple.

975
00:49:30,509 --> 00:49:31,718
I know these people.

976
00:49:31,802 --> 00:49:33,762
Sometimes you just have
to bend their arm...

977
00:49:33,845 --> 00:49:36,139
No! There's no bending.

978
00:49:36,223 --> 00:49:38,684
They saw the application,
and it wasn't good enough.

979
00:49:38,767 --> 00:49:40,435
End of story. Sometimes you lose.

980
00:49:40,519 --> 00:49:41,937
Lose?

981
00:49:42,020 --> 00:49:43,522
[scoffs] What are you...?

982
00:49:43,605 --> 00:49:44,856
No.

983
00:49:44,940 --> 00:49:49,236
We still have plenty of time for me
to call my friend who owes me.

984
00:49:49,319 --> 00:49:52,080
The only thing I should focus on
is that dude in the mirror, remember?

985
00:49:52,155 --> 00:49:53,448
This is different.

